<lb n="0188a13"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0188a14"/>
<lb n="0188a15"/><head type="no">No. 861</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0188a16"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0188002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】延享元年刊大正大學藏本，【甲】平安時代寫本高山寺藏豐山版</note>毘盧遮那五字真言修習儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0188a17"/>
<lb n="0188a18"/><byline type="Translator">三藏<note n="0188003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不空金剛＝金剛不空智奉【甲】</note><app n="0188003"><lem>不空金剛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">金剛不空智奉</rdg></app>　<note n="0188004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（奉）&M062485;＋詔【原】</note><sic n="0188004" corr="奉詔" resp="【原】">詔</sic>譯</byline>
<lb n="0188a19"/><p>夫修習成就毘盧遮那佛法。先應於閑淨處
<lb n="0188a20"/>以瞿摩夷塗地。香水散灑燒種種名香。散種
<lb n="0188a21"/>種時花。當於寂靜<note n="0188005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辦＝辭&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0188005" corr="辭" resp="【原】">辦</sic>喧鬧。清淨澡浴著新
<lb n="0188a22"/>淨衣結跏趺坐。或<note n="0188006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">依＋（求四種法座所謂息災增益敬　降伏）【甲】</note><app n="0188006"><lem>依</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">依求四種法座所謂息災增益敬　降伏</rdg></app>類而坐。息災吉祥<note n="0188007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝座【甲】＊</note><app n="0188007"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">座</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188a23"/>面向北。增益蓮花<app type="＊" source="0188007"><lem>坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>面向東。敬愛金剛<app type="＊" source="0188007"><lem>坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188a24"/>面向西。降伏蹲踞<app type="＊" source="0188007"><lem>坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>以&CB00560;押&CB00560;面向南。隨所
<lb n="0188a25"/>愛樂依方而坐。即以香泥塗手。於頂上合掌
<lb n="0188a26"/>禮敬一切諸佛。然於下方從風輪起想<note n="0188008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>字。
<lb n="0188a27"/>以二點嚴飾。如<note n="0188009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">金＋（剛）【甲】</note><app n="0188009"><lem>金</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">金剛</rdg></app>形放熾盛光。威猛赫<app><lem>奕</lem><rdg wit="【大】">弈</rdg></app>金
<lb n="0188a28"/>剛火焰壞破大地。上衝流出。則想此金剛火
<lb n="0188a29"/>焰焚燒自身。乃至灰<note n="0188010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謝＝&CB13789;【甲】</note><app n="0188010"><lem>謝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB13789;</rdg></app>隨四種法色。想灰成
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0861.0188b" n="0188b"/>
<lb n="0188b01"/>曼拏羅。即於曼荼羅中想一蓮花。於蓮花中
<lb n="0188b02"/>想<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>字。轉成金剛形。想己身為金剛所成</p>
<lb n="0188b03"/><p>即結三昧耶印　二手作三普吒掌。&CB00594;二大
<lb n="0188b04"/>指加持於五處。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188b05"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃阿三迷怛哩<note n="0188011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0188011"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三迷三
<lb n="0188b06"/>摩曳莎縛<note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note n="0188012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】</note><note n="0188012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔引〕－【甲】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188b07"/><p>次結法界印　二手作拳。二大指在掌中&CB00594;。
<lb n="0188b08"/>二頭指。想<note n="0188013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【甲】</note><app n="0188013"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>字於頂上。思惟真實義。一切
<lb n="0188b09"/>法塵不可得。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188b10"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃達<note n="0188014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝磨【甲】</note><app n="0188014"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">磨</rdg></app>馱<note n="0188015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">都＝&CB00418;【甲】</note><app n="0188015"><lem>都</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00418;</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;婆&CB00085;
<lb n="0188b11"/>俱<note n="0188016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吽＝唅【甲】</note><note n="0188016" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB00292;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">吽</rdg></app>＝唅【甲】</note><app n="0188016"><lem>&CB00292;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">唅</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188b12"/><p>次結次輪印　二手反相叉。<note n="0188017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝左【甲】</note><app n="0188017"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">左</rdg></app>大指在右手
<lb n="0188b13"/>掌中相著。觀自身為金剛薩埵。合以加持。真
<lb n="0188b14"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0188b15"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日<anchor id="fxT18p0188b03"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>喃<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日<anchor id="fxT18p0188b05"/>囉<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT18p0188b06"/>引</note>
<lb n="0188b16"/>怛摩俱唅</p>
<lb n="0188b17"/><p>次結甲冑印　二手三普吒掌。二頭指屈<note n="0188018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【甲】</note><app n="0188018"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">跓</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188b18"/>中指背上節。二大指並&CB00594;合在掌印五處。真
<lb n="0188b19"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0188b20"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>喃<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日羅迦<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>遮
<lb n="0188b21"/>吽</p>
<lb n="0188b22"/><p>則於自身前想大蓮華王。於蓮華中想金色
<lb n="0188b23"/>佉字。其佉字轉成婆伽梵大勤勇尊。住之三
<lb n="0188b24"/>摩地結劍印。即結如來鉤印奉請本尊。<note n="0188019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＋（手）【甲】</note><app n="0188019"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二手</rdg></app>內
<lb n="0188b25"/>相叉作拳。&CB00594;右頭指如鉤向身招之。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188b26"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃<note n="0188020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噁＝惡【甲】</note><app n="0188020"><lem>噁</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惡</rdg></app>娑<note n="0188021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔囉〕－【甲】</note><app n="0188021"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00085;怛<anchor id="fxT18p0188b09"/>囉&CB00425;羅
<lb n="0188b27"/>底訶多怛多<note n="0188022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00617;＋（多）【甲】，（黨）&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0188022"><lem><sic corr="＆CB00617；黨" resp="【原】">&CB00617;</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00617;多</rdg></app>俱舍&CB00155;地者哩耶&CB00425;哩布<anchor id="fxT18p0188b10"/>囉
<lb n="0188b28"/>迦娑<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188b29"/><p>聖眾來已。即奉閼伽　二手<note n="0188023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捧＋（器）【甲】</note><app n="0188023"><lem>捧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">捧器</rdg></app>當額想浴聖
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0861.0188c" n="0188c"/>
<lb n="0188c01"/>眾真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188c02"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃哦哦那三摩三摩娑<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188c03"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188c04"/><p>次獻敷座印　二手虛心合掌。散舒<note n="0188024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">屈＋（頭中名）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0188024" corr="屈頭中名" resp="【原】">屈</sic>六指
<lb n="0188c05"/>如蓮花形。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188c06"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<note n="0188025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喃＝南【甲】＊</note><app n="0188025"><lem>喃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">南</rdg></app>噁</p>
<lb n="0188c07"/><p>次結聖不動尊印　二手各作拳。各&CB00594;頭中
<lb n="0188c08"/>指。各以二大指押無名指小指。左手為鞘。右
<lb n="0188c09"/>手為刀。以刀左旋轉辟除諸魔障。右旋轉及
<lb n="0188c10"/>上下成方隅界。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188c11"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00718;戰拏摩訶嚧灑拏
<lb n="0188c12"/>薩叵吒耶吽怛<note n="0188026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＋（二合）&M062485;夾註【原】</note><sic n="0188026" corr="囉(二合)" resp="【原】">囉</sic>吒<note n="0188027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00292;＝吽【甲】</note><app n="0188027"><lem>&CB00292;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">吽</rdg></app>&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0188c13"/><p>復以刀印觸香花<note n="0188028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">求＝水【甲】，等&M062485;【原】</note><note n="0188028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">求＝水【甲】，＝等&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0188028"><lem><sic corr="等" resp="【原】">求</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">水</rdg></app>無垢令淨。以成加護置
<lb n="0188c14"/>於鞘中</p>
<lb n="0188c15"/><p>次結毘盧遮那五字劍印　二手合掌屈二頭
<lb n="0188c16"/>指相著。如劍形。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188c17"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃阿尾<anchor id="fxT18p0188c04"/>囉吽欠</p>
<lb n="0188c18"/><p>次結塗香印　右手掌向外。以左手。<note n="0188029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">握＝掘【甲】</note><app n="0188029"><lem>握</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">掘</rdg></app>右手
<lb n="0188c19"/>腕如環。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188c20"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app type="＊" source="0188025"><lem>喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>尾&CB02122;&CB00499;<note n="0188030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">巘＝獻【甲】</note><app n="0188030"><lem>巘</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">獻</rdg></app>塗納婆吠娑
<lb n="0188c21"/><app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188c22"/><p>次結花印　二手內相叉。仰掌頭指<note n="0188031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（相）＋著【甲】</note><app n="0188031"><lem>著</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">相著</rdg></app>。二大
<lb n="0188c23"/>指安頭指下節。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0188c24"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app type="＊" source="0188025"><lem>喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>摩訶每怛哩耶<note place="inline">二合</note>毘愈
<lb n="0188c25"/><note place="inline">二合</note>娜&CB00617;底娑<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188c26"/><p>次結燒香印　二手中指無名指小指背合
<lb n="0188c27"/>&CB00594;。頭指直&CB00594;傾相合。大指在頭指下節。真言
<lb n="0188c28"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0188c29"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app type="＊" source="0188025"><lem>喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>達摩&CB00499;<note n="0188032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;&CB00085;娜＝&CB03377;拏【甲】</note><app n="0188032"><lem>&CB00418;&CB00085;娜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB03377;拏</rdg></app>&CB00617;帝
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0861.0189a" n="0189a"/>
<lb n="0189a01"/><note n="0189001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0189001"><lem>莎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a02"/><p>次結飲食<note n="0189002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔真言〕－【甲】</note><app n="0189002"><lem>真言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>印　當合定惠。掌五輪互相
<lb n="0189a03"/>叉。是則持眾物。普通供養印</p>
<lb n="0189a04"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃阿<anchor id="fxT18p0189a03"/>囉<anchor id="fxT18p0189a04"/>囉迦<anchor id="fxT18p0189a05"/>囉<anchor id="fxT18p0189a06"/>囉<note n="0189003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">末＝未【甲】＊</note><app n="0189003"><lem>末</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">未</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a05"/>&CB00444;捺那<note n="0189004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迷＋（摩&CB00444;上聲娜泥摩訶麼理）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0189004" corr="迷摩＆CB00444；上聲娜泥摩訶麼理" resp="【原】">迷</sic>娑<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a06"/><p>次結<note n="0189005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">燈＋（明）【甲】</note><app n="0189005"><lem>燈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">燈明</rdg></app>印。右手作拳。中指直&CB00594;。頭指屈<note n="0189006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大捻＝捻大【甲】</note><app n="0189006"><lem>大
<lb n="0189a07"/>捻</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">捻大</rdg></app>。指博附中指。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189a08"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app type="＊" source="0188025"><lem>喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>多他&CB00617;多哩紙薩叵<anchor id="fxT18p0189a10"/>囉
<lb n="0189a09"/>拏<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>婆娑那哦哦那烏馱哩耶娑<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶
<lb n="0189a10"/><app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a11"/><p>所獻塗香花鬘燒香飲食燈明。隨四種法色。
<lb n="0189a12"/>而以供養。由五種供養印。成於聖眾集會普
<lb n="0189a13"/>遍香花等雲海供養</p>
<lb n="0189a14"/><p>次結圓滿印。二手虛心合掌安於頂上。真
<lb n="0189a15"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0189a16"/><p type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app type="＊" source="0188025"><lem>喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>噁尾娑摩曳娑叵<anchor id="fxT18p0189a15"/>囉呬
<lb n="0189a17"/>&CB00805;哦哦那劍達摩馱怛<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>迦舍三摩多耶娑
<lb n="0189a18"/><app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>怛他<note n="0189007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00617;＋（多）【甲】</note><app n="0189007"><lem>&CB00617;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00617;多</rdg></app><note n="0189008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跛＝跋&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0189008" corr="跋" resp="【原】">跛</sic>哩<note n="0189009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">剎＝殺【甲】</note><app n="0189009"><lem>剎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">殺</rdg></app>曼荼羅摩摩本惹<app type="＊" source="0189003"><lem>末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a19"/>禮拏怛他&CB00617;多地瑟&CB00109;那<app type="＊" source="0189003"><lem>末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未</rdg></app>禮那遮迷娑<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a20"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a21"/><p>由此真言印香花等雲海供養。如實<note n="0189010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＋（異）【甲】</note><app n="0189010"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">無異</rdg></app>即用
<lb n="0189a22"/>五字。從下體布至頂。地水火風空。即想自身
<lb n="0189a23"/>如金色毘盧遮那佛。<note n="0189011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍＋（身）&M062485;【原】，（放）&M062485;【原】</note>遍光明頭冠瓔珞身著
<lb n="0189a24"/>紗縠衣。即結劍印安於當心住三摩地。二手
<lb n="0189a25"/>持珠。合於掌中誦真言七遍。加持安<note n="0189012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【甲】</note><app n="0189012"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>頂
<lb n="0189a26"/>上。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189a27"/><p type="dharani">唵吠盧者那摩羅娑<app type="＊" source="0188008"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="＊" source="0188012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a28"/><p>然後二手當心。持珠念誦本尊<note n="0189013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（真）＋言【甲】</note><app n="0189013"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">真言</rdg></app>。遍數畢
<lb n="0189a29"/><note n="0189014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝竟【甲】</note><app n="0189014"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">竟</rdg></app>。安珠於掌中。頂上合掌迴向發願。以此
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0861.0189b" n="0189b"/>
<lb n="0189b01"/>功德當願眾生速證毘盧遮那佛。放念珠已。
<lb n="0189b02"/>然後結定印。端身正坐於<note n="0189015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頂＋（上）【甲】</note><app n="0189015"><lem>頂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">頂上</rdg></app>中想白色闇字。
<lb n="0189b03"/>於二目瞳人上想覽字。即微屈頭注心於胸
<lb n="0189b04"/>臆閒想圓<note n="0189016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＝明【甲】</note><app n="0189016"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">明</rdg></app>月輪。於月輪上布列五字。想阿
<lb n="0189b05"/>字在中央如黃金色。餘四字右旋而安</p>
<lb n="0189b06"/><p>五字真實義者</p>
<lb n="0189b07"/><p>阿字一切法本不生故　尾字思義一切法言
<lb n="0189b08"/>說不可得故　<anchor id="fxT18p0189b01"/>囉字一切法離塵故　訶字一
<lb n="0189b09"/>切法因不可得故　佉字一<note n="0189017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切＋（法）【甲】</note><app n="0189017"><lem>切</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">切法</rdg></app>如虛空<note n="0189018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不可得〕－【甲】</note><app n="0189018"><lem>不可
<lb n="0189b10"/>得</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>故。名為心念誦</p>
<lb n="0189b11"/><p>即結劍印誦七遍頂上散。復結五供養印。獻
<lb n="0189b12"/>閼伽讚歎。結不<note n="0189019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">動＋（尊）【甲】</note><app n="0189019"><lem>動</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">動尊</rdg></app>劍印。左旋解界。結三<note n="0189020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昧＋（耶）【甲】</note><app n="0189020"><lem>昧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">昧耶</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189b13"/>印安於頂上誦三遍。想奉送聖眾。禮佛而起
<lb n="0189b14"/>隨意經行。讀誦大乘方廣經典。以福迴施一
<lb n="0189b15"/>切眾生願速圓滿心所求。世閒出世閒悉地
<lb n="0189b16"/>成就也</p>
<lb n="0189b17"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>毘盧遮那念誦<note n="0189021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一卷＝經【甲】</note><app n="0189021"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">經</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
<lb n="0189b18"/><note n="0189022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔延享…焉〕五十五字－【甲】</note><app n="0189022" word-count="55"><lem><div1 type="W"><p>延享改元夏用亡弟僧尊隆遺財而刻是軌
<lb n="0189b19"/>以遂其宿志伏祈法乳永潤法界云　藤原
<lb n="0189b20"/>常香謹誌</p>
<lb n="0189b21"/><p>時延享元甲子秋八月念三豐山無等&CB00677;挍
<lb n="0189b22"/>焉</p></div1></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
</body></text></TEI.2>